accessibility.text: Main Goal: Attend his meeting at 9 am, 1st November 2018
Our App would send notifications to the user if his/her monthly-pass is expired
He arrives to the metro station, tries to validate his ticket by using the App on his phone
He gets a warning and now has three alternatives:
He charges his pass quickly using his payment methods added on the App
He can use on of his free tickets that he won through the milestone system
He can force the validation as our App allows a user to have a negative travel that can be payed later
He choses to pay his monthly fee
He validates the ticket, enters the metro and arrives on time to the meeting
